="grep"><a href="#grep" class="headerlink" title="grep"></a>grep</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">grep -r string &lt;dir&gt; <span class="comment">#&#x9012;&#x5F52;grep</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="&#x56FE;&#x7247;&#x67E5;&#x770B;"><a href="#&#x56FE;&#x7247;&#x67E5;&#x770B;" class="headerlink" title="&#x56FE;&#x7247;&#x67E5;&#x770B;"></a>&#x56FE;&#x7247;&#x67E5;&#x770B;</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">identify log.png</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="&#x6587;&#x4EF6;&#x6743;&#x9650;"><a href="#&#x6587;&#x4EF6;&#x6743;&#x9650;" class="headerlink" title="&#x6587;&#x4EF6;&#x6743;&#x9650;"></a>&#x6587;&#x4EF6;&#x6743;&#x9650;</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">chmod u+x s.sh  <span class="comment">#&#x7ED9;&#x811A;&#x672C;&#x4E00;&#x4E2A;&#x53EF;&#x6267;&#x884C;&#x7684;&#x6743;&#x9650;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="&#x8F93;&#x51FA;&#x91CD;&#x5B9A;&#x5411;"><a href="#&#x8F93;&#x51FA;&#x91CD;&#x5B9A;&#x5411;" class="headerlink" title="&#x8F93;&#x51FA;&#x91CD;&#x5B9A;&#x5411;"></a>&#x8F93;&#x51FA;&#x91CD;&#x5B9A;&#x5411;</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">2&gt;&amp;1 | tee log.txt</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><code>2&gt;</code> &#x6807;&#x51C6;&#x51FA;&#x9519;&#x91CD;&#x5B9A;&#x5411;</li><li><code>&amp;1</code> &#x65E0;&#x8BBA;&#x6807;&#x51C6;&#x8F93;&#x51FA;&#x5728;&#x54EA;&#x91CC;</li><li><code>tee</code> &#x628A;&#x8F93;&#x51FA;&#x4FE1;&#x606F;&#x540C;&#x65F6;&#x5199;&#x5230;&#x6587;&#x4EF6;&#x548C;&#x6807;&#x51C6;&#x8F93;&#x51FA;&#x4E2D;</li></ul><h3 id="&#x589E;&#x91CF;&#x4F20;&#x8F93;-rsync"><a href="#&#x589E;&#x91CF;&#x4F20;&#x8F93;-rsync" class="headerlink" title="&#x589E;&#x91CF;&#x4F20;&#x8F93;(rsync)"></a>&#x589E;&#x91CF;&#x4F20;&#x8F93;(rsync)</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="comment">#&#x5FFD;&#x7565;&#x67D0;&#x4E9B;&#x76EE;&#x5F55; -a &#x9012;&#x5F52; -v &#x663E;&#x793A;&#x8FDB;&#x5EA6;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">#&#x6E90;&#x8DEF;&#x5F84;&#x5982;&#x679C;&#x662F;&#x4E00;&#x4E2A;&#x76EE;&#x5F55;&#x7684;&#x8BDD;&#xFF0C;&#x5E26;&#x4E0A;&#x5C3E;&#x968F;&#x659C;&#x7EBF;&#x548C;&#x4E0D;&#x5E26;&#x5C3E;&#x968F;&#x659C;&#x7EBF;&#x662F;&#x4E0D;&#x4E00;&#x6837;&#x7684;&#xFF0C;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">#&#x4E0D;&#x5E26;&#x5C3E;&#x968F;&#x659C;&#x7EBF;&#x8868;&#x793A;&#x7684;&#x662F;&#x6574;&#x4E2A;&#x76EE;&#x5F55;&#x5305;&#x62EC;&#x76EE;&#x5F55;&#x672C;&#x8EAB;&#xFF0C;&#x5E26;&#x4E0A;&#x5C3E;&#x968F;&#x659C;&#x7EBF;&#x8868;&#x793A;&#x7684;&#x662F;&#x76EE;&#x5F55;&#x4E2D;&#x7684;&#x6587;&#x4EF6;&#xFF0C;&#x4E0D;&#x5305;&#x62EC;&#x76EE;&#x5F55;&#x672C;&#x8EAB;</span></div><div class="line">rsync -av source_dir --exclude=core user@remote:&lt;DIR&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="&#x8FDB;&#x7A0B;&#x67E5;&#x770B;&#x3001;&#x6740;&#x6B7B;"><a href="#&#x8FDB;&#x7A0B;&#x67E5;&#x770B;&#x3001;&#x6740;&#x6B7B;" class="headerlink" title="&#x8FDB;&#x7A0B;&#x67E5;&#x770B;&#x3001;&#x6740;&#x6B7B;"></a>&#x8FDB;&#x7A0B;&#x67E5;&#x770B;&#x3001;&#x6740;&#x6B7B;</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">ps -ef | grep caiwenpu</div><div class="line"><span class="built_in">kill</span> -s 9 &lt;PID&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="locate"><a href="#locate" class="headerlink" title="locate"></a>locate</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">locate file <span class="comment">#&#x67E5;&#x627E;&#x6587;&#x4EF6;&#xFF0C;&#x901F;&#x5EA6;&#x5FEB;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="ldd"><a href="#ldd" class="headerlink" title="ldd"></a>ldd</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">ldd ./_caffe.so | grep boost <span class="comment">#&#x67E5;&#x770B;&#x94FE;&#x63A5;&#x5E93;&#x4E2D;&#x4F9D;&#x8D56;&#x7684;&#x5E93;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="screen"><a href="#screen" class="headerlink" title="screen"></a>screen</h2><p>&#x4E3A;&#x4E86;&#x89E3;&#x51B3;ssh&#x8FDE;&#x63A5;&#x5230;&#x670D;&#x52A1;&#x5668;&#x4E4B;&#x540E;&#xFF0C;&#x7A0B;&#x5E8F;&#x8981;&#x8FD0;&#x884C;&#x5F88;&#x4E45;&#xFF0C;&#x6709;&#x65F6;&#x4F1A;&#x5BFC;&#x81F4;&#x4F1A;&#x8BDD;&#x7EC8;&#x7AEF;&#x800C;&#x65E0;&#x6CD5;&#x83B7;&#x5F97;&#x8FD0;&#x884C;&#x7ED3;&#x679C;&#xFF0C;&#x9700;&#x8981;&#x4F7F;&#x7528;screen&#x6765;&#x6062;&#x590D;&#x4E0A;&#x6B21;&#x7EC8;&#x7AEF;&#x7684;&#x4F1A;&#x8BDD;</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">screen -S Test <span class="comment">#&#x521B;&#x5EFA;&#x4F1A;&#x8BDD; &#x4F7F;&#x7528;ctrl+a+d&#x53EF;&#x4EE5;&#x79BB;&#x5F00;&#x4F1A;&#x8BDD;&#xFF0C;&#x800C;&#x4F1A;&#x8BDD;&#x4E0D;&#x4F1A;&#x7EC8;&#x6B62;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">screen -r Test <span class="comment">#&#x6062;&#x590D;&#x4F1A;&#x8BDD;</span></div><div class="line">screen -D -r Test <span class="comment">#&#x8E22;&#x6389;attached &#x8FDB;&#x7A0B;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">screen -ls <span class="comment">#&#x67E5;&#x770B;&#x5DF2;&#x7ECF;&#x521B;&#x5EFA;&#x7684;&#x4F1A;&#x8BDD;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>&#x5982;&#x679C;&#x5728;&#x6062;&#x590D;screen&#x7684;&#x65F6;&#x5019;&#x51FA;&#x73B0;There is no screen to be resumed matching Test<br>&#x8FD0;&#x884C;&#x547D;&#x4EE4;</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">screen -d Test</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>&#x5728;screen&#x4E2D;&#x4E0D;&#x80FD;&#x76F4;&#x63A5;&#x6EDA;&#x52A8;&#x5C4F;&#x5E55;&#xFF0C;&#x9700;&#x8981;&#x5728;<code>~/.screenrc</code>&#x6587;&#x4EF6;&#x4E2D;&#x6DFB;&#x52A0;&#xFF1A;</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="comment"># Enable mouse scrolling and scroll bar history scrolling</span></div><div class="line">termcapinfo xterm* ti@:te@</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="&#x6027;&#x80FD;&#x6D4B;&#x8BD5;"><a href="#&#x6027;&#x80FD;&#x6D4B;&#x8BD5;" class="headerlink" title="&#x6027;&#x80FD;&#x6D4B;&#x8BD5;"></a>&#x6027;&#x80FD;&#x6D4B;&#x8BD5;</h2><ul><li>I/O&#x8D1F;&#x8F7D;&#x67E5;&#x770B;</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">sudo apt-get install sysstate -y</div><div class="line">iostat -x 1 10</div><div class="line">``` </div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">idle &#x4F4E;&#x4E8E; 70%&#xFF0C;%util &#x8FBE;&#x5230; 95% &#x4EE5;&#x4E0A;&#x78C1;&#x76D8;&#x7684;&#x8D1F;&#x8F7D;&#x5C31;&#x6BD4;&#x8F83;&#x5927;&#x4E86;</div><div class="line"> iowait&#x7684;&#x503C;&#x6BD4;&#x8F83;&#x5927;&#xFF0C;&#x8BF4;&#x660E;&#x8BFB;&#x5199;&#x9891;&#x7E41;,cpu&#x7B49;&#x5F85;&#x65F6;&#x95F4;&#x957F;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">- &#x8FDB;&#x7A0B;&#x5360;&#x7528;&#x8D44;&#x6E90;&#x76D1;&#x6D4B;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">``` bash</div><div class="line"> pidstat -u -r -d -t 1        <span class="comment"># -d IO &#x4FE1;&#x606F;,</span></div><div class="line">                              <span class="comment"># -r &#x7F3A;&#x9875;&#x53CA;&#x5185;&#x5B58;&#x4FE1;&#x606F;</span></div><div class="line">                              <span class="comment"># -u CPU&#x4F7F;&#x7528;&#x7387;</span></div><div class="line">                              <span class="comment"># -t &#x4EE5;&#x7EBF;&#x7A0B;&#x4E3A;&#x7EDF;&#x8BA1;&#x5355;&#x4F4D;</span></div><div class="line">                              <span class="comment"># 1  1&#x79D2;&#x7EDF;&#x8BA1;&#x4E00;&#x6B21;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>CPU&#x901F;&#x5EA6;&#x6D4B;&#x8BD5;</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">time <span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;scale=5000; 4*a(1)&quot;</span> | bc -l -q</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>&#x78C1;&#x76D8;I/O&#x6D4B;&#x8BD5;</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">time dd <span class="keyword">if</span>=/dev/zero of=<span class="built_in">test</span> bs=1M count=4096</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="&#x538B;&#x7F29;&#x89E3;&#x538B;"><a href="#&#x538B;&#x7F29;&#x89E3;&#x538B;" class="headerlink" title="&#x538B;&#x7F29;&#x89E3;&#x538B;"></a>&#x538B;&#x7F29;&#x89E3;&#x538B;</h2><ul><li>.tar</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">tar xvf file.tar <span class="comment">#&#x89E3;&#x538B;</span></div><div class="line">tar cvf file.tar file <span class="comment">#&#x538B;&#x7F29;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>.gz</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">gunzip file.gz <span class="comment">#&#x89E3;&#x538B;</span></div><div class="line">gzip -d file.gz <span class="comment">#&#x89E3;&#x538B;</span></div><div class="line">gzip file <span class="comment">#&#x538B;&#x7F29;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>.tar.gz</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">tar zxvf file.tar.gz <span class="comment">#&#x89E3;&#x538B;</span></div><div class="line">tar zcvf file.tar.gz file <span class="comment">#&#x538B;&#x7F29;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>.tar.bz2</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">tar jxvf file.tar.bz2 <span class="comment">#&#x89E3;&#x538B;</span></div><div class="line">tar jcvf file.tar.bz2 file <span class="comment">#&#x538B;&#x7F29;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>.zip</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">unzip file.zip <span class="comment">#&#x89E3;&#x538B;</span></div><div class="line">zip file.zip file <span class="comment">#&#x538B;&#x7F29;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>.rar</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">rar x file.rar <span class="comment">#&#x89E3;&#x538B;</span></div><div class="line">rar a file.rar file <span class="comment">#&#x538B;&#x7F29;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="NVIDIA-&#x9A71;&#x52A8;&#x5B89;&#x88C5;"><a href="#NVIDIA-&#x9A71;&#x52A8;&#x5B89;&#x88C5;" class="headerlink" title="NVIDIA &#x9A71;&#x52A8;&#x5B89;&#x88C5;"></a>NVIDIA &#x9A71;&#x52A8;&#x5B89;&#x88C5;</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">sudo service lightdm stop <span class="comment">#&#x5173;&#x95ED;&#x56FE;&#x5F62;&#x754C;&#x9762;</span></div><div class="line">chmod +x *.run</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="comment">#&#x89E3;&#x51B3;nvidia-smi &#x51FA;&#x73B0;&#x6162;&#x7684;&#x95EE;&#x9898;</span></div><div class="line">sudo nvidia-persistenced --persistence-mode</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="Tips"><a href="#Tips" class="headerlink" title="Tips"></a>Tips</h2><p>The <code>*-dev</code> packages most often contain the headers related to a library&#x2019;s interface.</p><h1 id="MAC-&#x547D;&#x4EE4;"><a href="#MAC-&#x547D;&#x4EE4;" class="headerlink" title="MAC &#x547D;&#x4EE4;"></a>MAC &#x547D;&#x4EE4;</h1><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="built_in">command</span> + space &#x6253;&#x5F00;Spotlight&#x641C;&#x7D22;</div><div class="line"><span class="built_in">command</span> + Enter &#x6253;&#x5F00;&#x6240;&#x5728;&#x6587;&#x4EF6;&#x5939;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">ls -l filename <span class="comment">#&#x67E5;&#x770B;&#x8F6F;&#x94FE;&#x63A5;&#x6307;&#x5411;&#x7684;&#x5B9E;&#x9645;&#x6587;&#x4EF6;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>HomeBrew&#x5B89;&#x88C5;&#x7684;&#x7B2C;&#x4E09;&#x65B9;&#x5305;&#x5728; /usr/local/Cellar/ &#x76EE;&#x5F55;&#x4E0B;<br>python2.7&#x7684;&#x8DEF;&#x5F84;&#x4E3A;&#xFF1A;(&#x7CFB;&#x7EDF;&#x81EA;&#x5E26;)<br>/System/Library/Frameworks/Python.framework/Versions/2.7<br>python3.5&#x7684;&#x8DEF;&#x5F84;&#x4E3A;&#xFF1A;&#xFF08;&#x7528;&#x6237;&#x5B89;&#x88C5;&#xFF09;<br>/Library/Frameworks/Python.framework/Versions/3.5  </p><p><img src="/2017/10/25/hello-world/running.png" alt="logo"></p>]]></content>
    
